sequenceDiagram
    autonumber
    actor AJ as 🏢 Admin Jasa
    actor V as ✔ Verifikator<br/>(4 step)
    participant SYS as Sistem<br/>TagihanJasaController
    participant DB as DB tagihan_jasas
    participant WF as WorkflowService
    participant BTN as BtnVirtualAccountService
    participant WA as WhatsappService
    actor M as 👤 Mitra
    participant CB as BTN VA Callback
    participant PSS as PiutangSyncService
    participant BKU as 💰 transaksi_penerimaan<br/>+ buku_kas_umum
    actor BP as 💰 Bendahara<br/>Penerimaan

    rect rgb(239, 246, 255)
    Note over AJ,SYS: Tahap 1 — Pembuatan (Admin Jasa)
    AJ->>SYS: POST /tagihan-jasa (store)
    SYS->>DB: insert TagihanJasa<br/>status=VERIFIKASI_KOORDINATOR
    SYS->>WF: startWorkflow('TAGIHAN_JASA')
    WF-->>DB: workflow_instance IN_PROGRESS<br/>+ 4 approvals
    end

    rect rgb(254, 252, 232)
    Note over V,DB: Tahap 2 — Verifikasi berjenjang
    loop 4 step (Koord → Kasi → Kasubag → KPA)
        V->>SYS: approve / reject
        SYS->>WF: approveCurrentStep / rejectCurrentStep
        SYS->>DB: update status VERIFIKASI_* /<br/>DISETUJUI / DITOLAK
    end
    end

    rect rgb(236, 253, 245)
    Note over AJ,M: Tahap 3 — Finalisasi & Publish (Admin Jasa)
    AJ->>SYS: upload Surat Pengantar Final TTD
    SYS->>DB: status_dokumen_pengantar=SUDAH_DITANDATANGANI
    AJ->>SYS: POST publish + wa_tujuan
    SYS->>BTN: createVirtualAccount(tagihan)
    BTN-->>SYS: nomor VA + expired_at
    SYS->>DB: status=PUBLISHED, nomor_va, jatuh_tempo
    SYS->>PSS: syncFromPublished()
    PSS->>BKU: insert transaksi_penerimaan UNPAID
    SYS->>WA: sendMessage(link + VA)
    WA->>M: WhatsApp link tagihan + VA
    end

    rect rgb(245, 243, 255)
    Note over M,BP: Tahap 4 — Pembayaran & Pencatatan (Bendahara Penerimaan)
    BP->>BKU: monitor piutang UNPAID<br/>(menu Piutang)
    alt Pembayaran via VA BTN (otomatis)
        M->>M: Bayar via VA BTN
        CB->>BTN: handlePaymentCallback(payload)
        BTN->>DB: status=LUNAS, tanggal_lunas
        BTN->>PSS: syncFromLunas()
        PSS->>BKU: update piutang PAID
        PSS->>BKU: insert BKU DEBIT_MASUK<br/>saldo + nominal
        BTN->>WA: sendLunasNotification
        WA->>M: WhatsApp konfirmasi lunas
    else Pembayaran offline / manual (Admin Jasa)
        AJ->>SYS: POST markAsPaid
        SYS->>DB: status=LUNAS
        SYS->>PSS: syncFromLunas() (idempoten)
        SYS->>WA: sendLunasNotification
    end
    BP->>BKU: verifikasi pencatatan piutang & BKU<br/>(menu BKU + Buku Pembantu Bank)
    end
